<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-19 00:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8335 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STARR-REPORT-NYT &LR;      11-19 1052
