<HEADER>
A8361 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FRONTPAGE-ADVISORY-NY     11-19 0057
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FRONTPAGE-ADVISORY-NYT </SLUG>
  
(nk) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Editors:
</P>
<P>
   A 1st Ld-Writethru to CT-PATRIOTS-STADIUM, with Gov. Rowland
saying the Patriots have agreed to move to Connecticut, will move
within 10 minutes. It is an added starter on The New York Times
front page. It replaces NY-GUGGENHEIM-MUSEUM.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
