   CIR-GAME-SICKNESS (Undated) _ Technology that makes you sick.
seizures, motion sickness, a woman who takes dramamine just so she
can play Quake. By Katie Hafner.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-COMPUTER-COLUMN (Las Vegas) _ What's cool at Comdex, the
giant Las Vegas computer show. In brief, everything is getting
smaller, and thinner, and smaller and thinner. By Peter H. Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-GEEK-NOTES (Undated) _ Techno news and notes: Fewer
electronic shoppers than you might think; talk shows on the web;
and electronic help to keep you from backing your Suburban into the
parking garage wall. By Ian Austin.
