   CIR-SHOGO-GAMES (Undated) _ Shogo: A Japanese shooter that's
violent, melodramatic and silly. High camp comes to the death
match. By J.D. Herz.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-PAINTING-ROBOT (Undated) _ A painting robot that you can run
remotely from your home, through the miracle of the world wide web.
Then your paintings get posted for all to see. By David Kushner.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-QUAKE-CHAMPION (Undated) _ In San Francisco, Thresh and
Immortal go for the gold in a championship Quake death match. In
other words, computer gaming goes professional. Our reporter is on
the scene, as are some of the competitors' parents. By Matt
Richtel.
