A8769 &Cx1f; tab-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ADVISORY-LATINTRADE-N     11-19 0188
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ADVISORY-LATINTRADE-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    MEXICO'S WAR ON CRIME. The Mexican crime wave has become a
national obsession and an added cost of doing business south of the
border. But President Zedillo's initiative is trying to take a bite
out of crime.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MEXICO-CRIME-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f'' financial and
``i'' international files.
