figurines, sculptures and statuettes made of terra cotta,
earthenware, glass, porcelain, resin, crystal and china, wastepaper
baskets, soap dishes, toothbrush holders, china ornaments, wind
chimes, plastic coasters, cocktail picks, comb cases, commemorative
plates, cookie cutters, cosmetic brushes, corkscrews, soap dishes,
