dinnerware, candlesticks not of precious metal, coffee services not
of precious metal; men's, women's, and children's clothing and
athletic wear, namely, underwear, rainwear, sleepwear, hosiery,
footwear, belts, suspenders, caps, head wear, knit caps, athletic
shoes, bathrobes, belts, coats, shirts, gloves, hats, jackets,
jogging suits, leather jackets, mittens, pajamas, scarves, shorts,
pants, skirts, dresses, slippers, socks, sweaters, swim wear, tank
tops, ties, vests, windbreakers, masquerade costumes and masks and
accessories sold in connection therewith, children's footwear,
