Brennan, Mariner/Houghton Mifflin, paper, $13
</P>
<P>
   DIANE, A Signature Life, By Diane Von Furstenberg with Linda
Bird Francke, Simon &AMP; Schuster, $25
</P>
<P>
   HISTORY IN OUR TIME, By David Cannadine, Yale, $25
</P>
<P>
