   11/20 COLOR WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map in
color.
</P>
<P>
   11/20 B&AMP;W WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map.
</P>
<P>
   11/20 CLOUD COVER -- 15p x 1 7/8 -- Cloud cover each day.
</P>
