worked the first time without a hitch.
</P>
<P>
   The Card Scan software is quite good as a stand alone contact
manager. While it lacks the functionality of the full-featured
programs, I found it wonderful as a sort of clearing house for
database clean up. On occasions, a hot sync will fail during a
normal Palm Pilot transfer, and when it finally works again, I can
end up with duplicate entries. The Card Scan software has a ``find
duplicate'' function and it took no time to get rid of the excess.
A re-sync and all my databases matched.
</P>
<P>
   Two pleasant things developed during this evaluation, I found
the card of a missing friend and my desk drawer is now half empty.
</P>
