sticking with three WRs in red zone, juggling OL, juggling RBs),
and why they might or might not work. Together they paint a picture
of haplessness, of a team without real alternatives.
</P>
<P>
   By Clare Farnsworth. (story will move in the ``s'' category)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-HUSKIES (Seattle) These fifth-year seniors are the remains
of the first Husky class hit by NCAA sanctions. Six of the 15 left
within 2-3 years in the Washington program. We track some of them
down, for perspective on Washington's troubles.
</P>
<P>
   By Bud Withers. (story will move in the ``s'' category)
