<P>
   IMPEACH-RDP (Washington) _ Kenneth Starr opened the third
presidential impeachment inquiry in the nation's history Thursday
by charging before a bitterly divided House Judiciary Committee
that President Clinton ``misused his authority and power'' to
impede civil and criminal cases against him. By Alison Mitchell.
</P>
