<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-19 20:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0068 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ROSENTHAL-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      11-19 0736
