<HEADLINE>
MIDEAST NEIGHBORS HAVE FIRST DISCUSSION OF CROSS-BORDER TRADE 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication notice: also filed in category `i') 
(smw) 
 By WILLIAM A. ORME Jr.   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
